name: WorldTao
description: WorldTAO is an RWA subnet that utilizes AI Bittensor technology to develop an ecosystem for converting real-life assets into digital formats, serving the needs of digital asset management and investment. The primary mission of WorldTAO is to forge an ecosystem that supports decentralized applications (DApps) in tokenizing and factionalizing RWAs into NFTs, ensuring a secure, efficient, and scalable framework.
